# ============================================================================
# PROJECT SPECIFIC NOTES
# ============================================================================

# IMPORTANT: DO NOT add these to .gitignore:
# - Assets/**/*.meta files (Unity REQUIRES these for asset management!)
# - ProjectSettings/*.asset files (needed for Unity configuration)
# - Packages/manifest.json & packages-lock.json (dependency management)
# - All .cs script files (your source code!)
# - All .shader, .shadergraph files (rendering pipeline)
# - Scene files (*.unity)
# - Prefabs (*.prefab)
# - Materials (*.mat)

# Repository structure:
# - Assets/ = Unity game assets (tracked)
# - ProjectSettings/ = Unity configuration (tracked)
# - Packages/ = Unity package dependencies (tracked)
